OL,3,CWatchdog cracks down on ads for
OL,4,Cprescription-only weight-loss drugs
OL,6,FThe advertising watchdog has launched
OL,7,Fa crackdown on the advertising of
OL,8,Fprescription-only weight-loss
OL,9,Fmedication, warning anyone doing so is
OL,10,Fbreaking the law.
OL,12,FThe Advertising Standards Authority
OL,13,F(ASA) said a search in January found
OL,14,Faround 1,800 unique paid-for weight-
OL,15,Floss ads which were identified as
OL,16,Fpotentially advertising a prescription-
OL,17,Fonly medicine (POM).
