OL,3,CWatchdog cracks down on ads for
OL,4,Cprescription-only weight-loss drugs
OL,6,FIt has published a joint Enforcement
OL,7,FNotice with the Medicines and
OL,8,FHealthcare products Regulatory Agency
OL,9,F(MHRA) and General Pharmaceutical
OL,10,FCouncil (GPhC), making clear that ads
OL,11,Ffor named weight-loss POMs are
OL,12,Fprohibited, including online, on
OL,13,Fsocial media and by influencers.
OL,15,FAny remaining ads must be removed
OL,16,Fimmediately, it warned.
OL,18,FIn December, the ASA warned businesses
OL,19,Fand individuals who were targeting
OL,20,Fmembers of the public with ads for the
OL,21,Fmedicines.
