OL,3,CWatchdog cracks down on ads for
OL,4,Cprescription-only weight-loss drugs
OL,6,FIt said: "No-one operating in this
OL,7,Findustry can say they have not been
OL,8,Fwarned that weight-loss prescription-
OL,9,Fonly medicines must not be promoted to
OL,10,Fthe public."
OL,12,FThe ASA said it had launched 12
OL,13,Finvestigations which were currently
OL,14,Funder way into whether ads were
OL,15,Fpromoting weight-loss POMs, including
OL,16,Fpaid-for online ads and affiliate and
OL,17,Finfluencer marketing.
OL,19,FIt continued to keep a "close watch"
OL,20,Fon the sector and did not rule out
OL,21,Ffurther investigations.
