OL,3,CWatchdog cracks down on ads for
OL,4,Cprescription-only weight-loss drugs
OL,6,FASA regulatory projects manager Jess
OL,7,FTye said: "We have made clear from the
OL,8,Foutset of this initiative that
OL,9,Fadvertising weight-loss prescription-
OL,10,Fonly medicines to the public is
OL,11,Fagainst the law and the advertising
OL,12,Frules."
