OL,3,CWatchdog cracks down on ads for
OL,4,Cprescription-only weight-loss drugs
OL,6,FDionne Spence, chief enforcement
OL,7,Fofficer at the GPhC, said: "It is
OL,8,Fvital that people receive prescription-
OL,9,Fonly medicines, such as those used for
OL,10,Fweight management, only after having
OL,11,Fan appropriate consultation, and when
OL,12,Ftheir prescriber has independently
OL,13,Fverified that the medicines are
OL,14,Fclinically appropriate for them.
OL,16,F"Adverts and special price offers
OL,17,Fshould not be used for prescription-
OL,18,Fonly medicines as they are likely to
OL,19,Fpromote the specific POM.
