OL,3,CWatchdog cracks down on ads for
OL,4,Cprescription-only weight-loss drugs
OL,6,F"GPhC inspectors will continue to
OL,7,Finspect pharmacies to ensure our
OL,8,Fstandards are being met and will be
OL,9,Flooking for evidence that our guidance
OL,10,Ffor registered pharmacies providing
OL,11,Fpharmacy services at a distance,
OL,12,Fincluding on the internet, is being
OL,13,Ffollowed.
OL,15,F"We will be working closely with our
OL,16,Fregulatory partners to ensure that
OL,17,Fprompt and proportionate action is
OL,18,Ftaken where necessary to protect the
OL,19,Fpublic."
